These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: marigold, amaryllis
1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Flower   | amaryllis | marigold |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: swimming, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2      |
| Sport   | swimming | skateboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-3::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: fuchsia, brown
1. the person who likes brown is on the left or right of the person who likes fuchsia##3
2. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Color   | brown | fuchsia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-4::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, roller
1. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |
| Transport   | roller | boat |

